{"tid":1924923,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"建制被趕　立會保安無抬人","createTime":"2020-03-14T04:10:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-14T05:42:15.000Z","uid":81228,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bb727dfb66b9e8354deecba98541bea71b2e981c","tid":1924923,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T04:10:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20200314/s00046/544e1791f640dbfc0d7a0963bab07c0c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20200314%2Fs00046%2F544e1791f640dbfc0d7a0963bab07c0c.jpg&h=1c6de422&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n建制派議員何君堯（中）噚日喺立法會內會上叫囂，畀主持內會嘅公民黨郭榮鏗命令佢離開，不過佢點都唔肯走，保安只係包圍佢，但無行動帶佢離開，畀民主派批評同以往抬泛民離場嘅手法有別。<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20200314/s00046/544e20a9b9abe51e0ad16c70e0c6a406.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20200314%2Fs00046%2F544e20a9b9abe51e0ad16c70e0c6a406.jpg&h=87db7557&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔少民主派喺立法會都有被抬走經驗，包括人民力量陳志全（圖）。（資料圖片）<br />\n<br />\n立法會內會噚日召開第13次特別會議，但仍未選出正副主席，緊接舉行財委會會議。主持內會嘅公民黨郭榮鏗（Dennis）過咗會議原定結束時間，仍然畀民主黨尹兆堅發言，引嚟財委會主席陳健波不滿，喺席上批評 Dennis冇準時交還會議室，Dennis話佢叫囂，命令佢馬上離開會議室；何君堯加入批評Dennis，同樣畀Dennis話佢喺位叫囂，逐離會議室。不過何君堯唔聽，更拍枱大叫「出去豬兜（咪兜）度講嘢啦豬兜」，衝出主席台批評Dennis濫權。民主派不滿保安冇抬走何君堯，話同對待民主派嘅做法有別。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>會議時間結束　郭榮鏗照畀尹兆堅發言惹不滿</strong><br />\n<br />\n民建聯周浩鼎同黃定光都加入戰團，企起身批評Dennis，同樣被要求離開會議廳，但兩人唔聽，保安亦無抬人。爭拗期間，已經離開會議廳嘅波哥又走返入嚟，畀公民黨陳淑莊發現大叫：「陳健波點解又可以入到嚟？」Dennis亦問「保安，你哋喺度做咩嘢？」周三財會，Dennis因形容波哥係「奴才」，畀波哥逐離場。<br />\n<br />\n內會上，建制泛民再為「武漢肺炎」字眼爭拗，泛民認為「武漢肺炎」肆虐，唔應該召開任何同抗疫無關嘅會議。建制派不滿泛民用「武漢肺炎」字眼，民建聯何俊賢話「病毒無地域和人群之分」，又問「十年後武漢人點樣抬起頭」，認為議員用詞係反映人格。公民黨郭家麒話，醫學上唔會因為病名而歧視一個地方，反問係咪要去信要求世衛叫「香港腳」做「真菌腳」。工黨張超雄亦問，「講武漢肺炎就無人格？係咪要跟足共產黨先有人格呢？」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20200314/s00002/1584125438976/%E3%80%90emily%E3%80%91%E4%BD%95%E5%90%9B%E5%A0%AF%E5%91%A8%E6%B5%A9%E9%BC%8E%E9%BB%83%E5%AE%9A%E5%85%89%E5%94%94%E8%B5%B0-%E9%99%B3%E5%81%A5%E6%B3%A2%E5%BD%88%E5%87%BA%E5%BD%88%E5%85%A5-4%E5%BB%BA%E5%88%B6%E8%A2%AB%E8%B6%95-%E7%AB%8B%E6%9C%83%E4%BF%9D%E5%AE%89%E7%84%A1%E6%8A%AC%E4%BA%BA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200314%2Fs00002%2F1584125438976%2F%25E3%2580%2590emily%25E3%2580%2591%25E4%25BD%2595%25E5%2590%259B%25E5%25A0%25AF%25E5%2591%25A8%25E6%25B5%25A9%25E9%25BC%258E%25E9%25BB%2583%25E5%25AE%259A%25E5%2585%2589%25E5%2594%2594%25E8%25B5%25B0-%25E9%2599%25B3%25E5%2581%25A5%25E6%25B3%25A2%25E5%25BD%2588%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%25BD%2588%25E5%2585%25A5-4%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E5%2588%25B6%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E8%25B6%2595-%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%259C%2583%25E4%25BF%259D%25E5%25AE%2589%25E7%2584%25A1%25E6%258A%25AC%25E4%25BA%25BA&d=B95HL5QQ1MLE%2FldfuzA7j0B1UtkZy1G9%2FYekDAkGV2Y%3D&h=94b96545\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200314%2Fs00002%2F1584125438976%2F%25E3%2580%2590emily%25E3%2580%2591%25E4%25BD%2595%25E5%2590%259B%25E5%25A0%25AF%25E5%2591%25A8%25E6%25B5%25A9%25E9%25BC%258E%25E9%25BB%2583%25E5%25AE%259A%25E5%2585%2589%25E5%2594%2594%25E8%25B5%25B0-%25E9%2599%25B3%25E5%2581%25A5%25E6%25B3%25A2%25E5%25BD%2588%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%25BD%2588%25E5%2585%25A5-4%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E5%2588%25B6%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E8%25B6%2595-%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%259C%2583%25E4%25BF%259D%25E5%25AE%2589%25E7%2584%25A1%25E6%258A%25AC%25E4%25BA%25BA&h=0cb93c68\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20200314/s00002/1584125438976/%E3%80%90emily%E3%80%91%E4%BD%95%E5%90%9B%E5%A0%AF%E5%91%A8%E6%B5%A9%E9%BC%8E%E9%BB%83%E5%AE%9A%E5%85%89%E5%94%94%E8%B5%B0-%E9%99%B3%E5%81%A5%E6%B3%A2%E5%BD%88%E5%87%BA%E5%BD%88%E5%85%A5-4%E5%BB%BA%E5%88%B6%E8%A2%AB%E8%B6%95-%E7%AB%8B%E6%9C%83%E4%BF%9D%E5%AE%89%E7%84%A1%E6%8A%AC%E4%BA%BA</a>"},{"pid":"29b69f913f7ff1c07f6c826e5c32700bf810478c","tid":1924923,"uid":298012,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T04:12:53.000Z","msg":"退休狗首選職業：保安"},{"pid":"19a440b0ecc1100221936fcd366c452bea6eb7f6","tid":1924923,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T05:35:08.000Z","msg":"何已完都選唔撚到？點解佢仲可以出現？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"109160aea86829d1f96ae44db1775061aab092cc","tid":1924923,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T05:42:15.000Z","msg":"自己友<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iqeHSBn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiqeHSBn.jpg&h=ab0b2641&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屍Ben Sir<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警務人員子女關注組<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1870807\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1870807</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}